PrecisAppointment of DIANE JACOVELLA of Gatineau, Quebec, Deputy Minister for International Development, styled Deputy Minister of International Development, to be concurrently Deputy Minister of Women and Gender Equality, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure, effective May 6, 2019.
